page.title: 17FASHION IN 1985
page.content:
CASUALS. Their clothes are a mass of designer labels such as Sergio,Tacchin,Geno, Cappel and Feeler and many more.How many different designer clothes you have depends on how much money you have,as they are very expensive ranging from twenty pounds for a jumper to forty pounds for a pair of Nike boots. MODS. These have been around for years,but are still quite popular,they wear parker coats which are dark green,they are big ,baggy coats and they decorate these with beer mats and badges.They have quite a range of their own clothes,their clothes are difficult to purchase and expensive.
